{
  "texts": [
    "As Gen AI continues to evolve and proliferate, it has significant potential for positive impact.",
    "But it also raises concerns that merit examination.",
    "For example, Gen AI solutions grapple with potential infringement of intellectual property rights (IPR).",
    "This concern is likely more relevant to Gen AI solutions using general LLMs, which draw from a wide body of content.",
    "When creating new output in response to user prompts, Gen AI potentially creates output that may infringe on IPR (Susarla, 2024; also see Table 2), which represents a serious concern, especially in creative contexts."
  ]
}